name: The Sunflour Bakery & Eatery (The Sunflour)
text: Very knowledgeable about everyone of their products. Friendly and helpful staff. Their prices are very reasonable. If you have not been by lately stop in they are well stocked for spring.

name: NaNa Dobbs
text: Found what I needed. Other places were out of banana pepper and jalapeno plants. They had them. And got some seeds too. They were very helpful and got seeds for me.

resp.text: We are glad you got what you needed! Thanks!

name: Connie Sparman
text: Nice friendly people working there. And a great variety of seeds and plants.

name: Jennifer Shoemaker
text: These are some wonderful people! I'm proud they are a part of my community! They always load all the heavy items for you and my back really appreciated that!

name: Stephena Talley
text: Good people always give good service good selection of seeds chemicals and supplies for fruit and vegetable farmers good knowledge

name: Gena Bradley
text: Always able to assist you with any of your supply needs.

name: Stephen Todd
text: Greg and the staff have helped me grow in knowledge in the farming business. Great people and products.

name: Raymond Sloan
text: I needed some turnip green seeds

resp.text: Thanks for coming by! We hope you enjoyed your visit!

name: Todd Nichols
text: Not good service ,an act stuck up rather than helpful I suggest Chambers

name: J C
text: Get your fertilizer, feed and supplies here.
